s.  No one argues this point.<br><br>Finally, the evolution completes itself. . .you become ~An Assassin~.  A Respected killer. . .your services become globally sought after.  <br><br>Id say the Rogue evolution was better thought out than the <br><br>&quot;Gee, golly - im a thief watch me pick a pocket and get my ass kicked if im caught. . .this is soo exciting - WHAT!  Why the hell would i wanna be a damage dealer~!   This is stoopid!  We all know sneeking around the Avatar of War is a much greater contribution than fargin constant stream of elite Damage. . .OK i hate myself. . .im gonna complain and roll a beastmaster cause thats Definatly the endgame baybe&quot; mentality<br><br>Shamroc - Assassin of the White Rose<br>Blades of Wrath<br>Torvonite<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ushariin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shariin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/15/02 9:28:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22289.topic&index=20>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The &quot;Rogue&quot; idea is Right - the &quot;Thief&qu</span><hr size=1> When I created Shariin, what I had in mind was neither thief or assassin.  She was to be a Scout, with a duty to her people, yet flighty and whimsical.  She was to be a con artist, using her good looks and quick wit to get what she wanted and disappear before the mark knew what hit 'em.<br><br>I never intended for her to be a great fighter, I never intended her to take on the personality of a stone-cold killer.  I di